_images/2050787216/image_2050787216.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745776-darden-restaurants-improved-outlook-but-valuation-dont-look-cheap-rating-upgrade-to-hold", "pub_date": "2024-12-21 14:19:02", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4745773", "title": "Grupo Financiero Galicia: Still Room For Further Share Price Growth", "description": "<figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2025129317/image_2025129317.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Scenic Aerial View of Buenos Aires Urban Landscape and Architecture\" data-id=\"2025129317\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"984px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2025129317/image_2025129317.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2025129317/image_2025129317.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2025129317/image_2025129317.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2025129317/image_2025129317.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2025129317/image_2025129317.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2025129317/image_2025129317.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2025129317/image_2025129317.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2025129317/image_2025129317.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Nikada</p></figcaption></figure><div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>Grupo Finan